nodes.title: README.TXT
widgets_values:
Abominable Workflows v3
=======================
https://civitai.com/models/420163/abominable-workflows

REQUIRED FILES
--------------
 To use this workflow, you need to install the following models in ComfyUI.
 Place them in the specified directories:

 <your_comfyui_dir> / models / checkpoints /
   > PixArt-Sigma-1024.safetensors
   > Photon-Refiner.safetensors

 <your_comfyui_dir> / models / clip /
   > T5-Encoder-Q5_K_M.gguf

 <your_comfyui_dir> / models / vae /
   > PixArt-Sigma-VAE.safetensors

 All four files can be downloaded from:
   https://huggingface.co/martin-rizzo/AbominableWorkflow/tree/main

REQUIRED NODES
--------------
 This workflow also requires the following custom nodes:

   > ComfyUI_ExtraModels
     https://github.com/city96/ComfyUI_ExtraModels

   > ComfyUI-GGUF
     https://github.com/city96/ComfyUI-GGUF

   > ComfyUI-Crystools
     https://github.com/crystian/ComfyUI-Crystools

 For detailed installation instructions for these nodes, please refer to the main page of Abominable Workflows.

OUTPUT IMAGES
-------------
 Generated images will be automatically saved in:
    <your_comfyui_dir> / output / abominable /

IMAGE SIZE
----------
 This workflow uses PixArt-1024 beyond its recommended size. For optimal quality, consider using the values provided by PixArt's authors:

    9:21 =  640 x 1536
    9:16 =  768 x 1344
    4:5  =  896 x 1152
    2:3  =  832 x 1216
    1:1  = 1024 x 1024
    3:2  = 1216 x  832
    5:4  =  896 x 1152
   21:9  = 1536 x  640
   16:9  = 1344 x  768

ABOMINABLE WORKFLOWS IN V3
--------------------------
  > abominable_1GIRL_.json
  > abominable_DARKFAN80_.json
  > abominable_GHIBLI_.json
  > abominable_INK_.json
  > abominable_MILO_.json
  > abominable_PHOTO_.json
  > abominable_POLAROID_.json
  > classic_abominable_spaghetti.json

nodes.title: PIXEL personal tips (but feel free to experiment)
widgets_values:
* Seed              : random
 * Guidance          : 4.0     [ 3.0 - 5.0 ]
 * Refiner intensity : 14      [ 12  - 18  ]
 * Refiner attention : empty   < focuses refiner on specific objects
 * Refiner variation : 0       < creates alternative versions with different details

Increasing 'Guidance' makes the pixel art look more old-school.
Lowering 'Guidance' produces more detailed pixel art with more colors.

For more information about Abominable Workflows:
https://civitai.com/models/420163
